  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed extension, by reason of its inappropriate siting, size and scale is considered to form an overly dominant & discordant additions to the host property and the surrounding context and the UPVC window additions would also be out of character, non-contextual in appearance for the ancillary store building and inappropriate in their siting. The proposal would present as incongruous within the surrounding area and would unacceptably impact upon the open backland character of the immediate surrounding area. The proposal is therefore contrary to Policy PLAN1 of Islington's Strategic and Development Management Policies (2023) and the guidance in Islington Urban Design Guide (2017)."
